      "content": "wait sorry what? I think I misread that. anyway, back to the house—what happens if the home inspection comes back and shows some major issues, like a cracked foundation? do I get that earnest money back or is it stuck in escrow?",
      "source": "evaluator",
      "targeted_response_start": "",
